'''The Crypt''' is the [[bar (location)|bar]] located in the north-west corner of [[Darkmeyer]]. It is run by the [[vampyre]] [[Despoina Callidra]], who sells [[blood pint]]s, a beverage made of alcohol-infused blood, at the price of 2 coins. It is the only bar where blood pints can be acquired.

Players will have to complete the [[Sins of the Father]] quest and be wearing a set of [[vyre noble clothing]] in order to purchase blood pints in the bar.

